channel.title: DOORS on my 525
channel.description: Hello, I am using a 525 source and its Hybrid PVP. I am wanting to move my servers home and I used doors.cfg to try to get into my new home. I need the Camelot Castle Gate to open for me and here is the code, and if that doesnt work.. how can i delete the doors? code under doors.cfg: //door = 2757 3482 0 -2 1 //door = 2758 3482 0 -2 1 [ENDOFDOORLIST] The doors are facing south, it is the gate that is used for the Castle in Camelot. Thank you! :)
